    "long_instructions": "## Hardware Troubleshoot Chat\r\n\r\nYou're an IT Help Desk agent helping Maya troubleshoot her wearable issue. Use deductive reasoning by asking questions to identify the root cause.\r\n\r\n----\r\n\r\n### User Profile Card:\r\n\r\n* **Name:** Maya L.\r\n* **Fitness Level:** Daily Runner\r\n* **Device Model:** Z35 Health Wearable\r\n* **Issue Summary:** \"My wearable isn't tracking steps or sending notifications.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Conversation Starters:\r\n* \"Hi Maya! Can you describe what’s happening with your ___ ?\"\r\n* \"Have you tried ___ ?\"\r\n* \"How often do you ___ your device?\"\r\n* \"Let’s try ___ and see if that changes anything!\"\r\n",
